{"type":"message","id":"58f01140","parentId":"ad58e8ae","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:41:55.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否能看到用于操作 limo 小车的 skill。让我查看一下 available_skills 中是否有相关的 skill。\n\n从 available_skills 中我看到有一个：\n```\n<skill>\n  <name>ROS-limo-car</name>\n  <description>用于控制 LIMO 机器人的 skill。可获取机器人状态（里程计/激光雷达/电池）、控制运动（前进/后退/转向）、执行单点或多点导航、拍照。通过 limo_ws_client.py 工具脚本调用，所有输出为 JSON 格式。</description>\n  <location>~/.openclaw/skills/ROS-limo-car/SKILL.md</location>\n</skill>\n```\n\n是的，我可以看到这个 skill！让我告诉用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以看到！有一个 `ROS-limo-car` skill：\n\n**功能包括：**\n- 获取机器人状态（里程计/激光雷达/电池）\n- 控制运动（前进/后退/转向）\n- 执行单点或多点导航\n- 拍照\n\n通过 `limo_ws_client.py` 工具脚本调用，输出为 JSON 格式。\n\n要我读取这个 skill 的详细说明吗？或者你想直接用它来操作小车？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":6158,"output":390,"cacheRead":5696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12244,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774096905876}}
