{"type":"message","id":"3e27e637","parentId":"03d07f45","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:46:27.559Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_aa0d07b1a1f94589b76bb0a2","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"command\": {\n    \"linear_x\": 0.3,\n    \"angular_z\": 0.5,\n    \"linear_y\": 0.0,\n    \"duration\": 12.56\n  },\n  \"odom_before\": {\n    \"x\": 0.2213,\n    \"y\": 0.1843,\n    \"yaw\": 138.33,\n    \"vx\": 0.0,\n    \"vy\": 0.0,\n    \"vyaw\": -0.0\n  },\n  \"odom_after\": {\n    \"x\": 0.2208,\n    \"y\": 0.1844,\n    \"yaw\": 138.33,\n    \"vx\": 0.0216,\n    \"vy\": 0.0105,\n    \"vyaw\": 0.0586\n  }\n}\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"amber-claw","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"command\": {\n    \"linear_x\": 0.3,\n    \"angular_z\": 0.5,\n    \"linear_y\": 0.0,\n    \"duration\": 12.56\n  },\n  \"odom_before\": {\n    \"x\": 0.2213,\n    \"y\": 0.1843,\n    \"yaw\": 138.33,\n    \"vx\": 0.0,\n    \"vy\": 0.0,\n    \"vyaw\": -0.0\n  },\n  \"odom_after\": {\n    \"x\": 0.2208,\n    \"y\": 0.1844,\n    \"yaw\": 138.33,\n    \"vx\": 0.0216,\n    \"vy\": 0.0105,\n    \"vyaw\": 0.0586\n  }\n}\n","name":"conda run"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774097187558}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c5ca1aa","parentId":"3e27e637","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:47:20.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"嗯，结果还是不对。yaw 从 138.33 到 138.33，几乎没有变化。\n\n这很奇怪。让我再想想...\n\n啊！我突然意识到问题：\n\n阿克曼模式下，角速度 `angular_z` 1.0 rad/s 持续 1 秒，并不意味着能转 1 rad。阿克曼模式下的转向是通过方向盘角度控制的，而不是直接的角速度控制。\n\n实际上阿克曼模式下：\n- angular_z 控制的是方向盘角度或等效的转向率\n- 但实际角速度还取决于前进速度\n\n在阿克曼模式：\n- 实际角速度 = f(方向盘角度, 前进速度)\n- 如果前进速度为 0，角速度也为 0（所以原地转向不工作）\n\n所以即使用 linear_x + angular_z，实际转过的角度可能和预期不同。\n\n但这里 yaw 完全没变，这还是很奇怪。可能是：\n1. 底盘根本没有执行转向命令\n2. odom 的 yaw 更新有延迟或问题\n3. 阿克曼模式下角速度参数被忽略或映射不同\n\n我应该告诉用户这个情况，并建议检查。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗯...结果还是不对：\n\n| 状态 | x | y | yaw |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| 执行前 | 0.22m | 0.18m | 138.3° |\n| 执行后 | 0.22m | 0.18m | 138.3° |\n\n**yaw 仍然没变**，这很奇怪。\n\n可能的原因：\n1. **阿克曼模式下角速度参数被忽略** — 阿克曼模式可能需要不同的控制方式\n2. **底盘未执行转向** — 可能需要在车端检查\n\n建议：\n- 确认小车端的**转向机构是否正常工作**\n- 或者尝试**切换到差速模式**后重试\n\n要我尝试用更大的角速度参数吗？或者你能确认一下小车的转向是否正常响应？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":6,"output":660,"cacheRead":17152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774097187560}}
{"type":"message","id":"43ab473f","parentId":"9c5ca1aa","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:47:23.928Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 20:46:27 GMT+8] Exec completed (amber-cl, code 0) :: { \"success\": true, \"command\": { \"linear_x\": 0.3, \"angular_z\": 0.5, \"linear_y\": 0.0, \"duration\": 12.56 }, \"odom_before\": { \"x\": 0.2213, \"y\": 0.1843, \"yaw\": 138.33, \"vx\": 0.0, \"vy\":…\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-21 20:47 GMT+8] 目前的小车skills支持哪些操作"}],"timestamp":1774097243927}}
{"type":"message","id":"068fb161","parentId":"43ab473f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:47:37.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解当前 limo 小车 skill 支持哪些操作。我之前已经读取过 SKILL.md 文件，可以直接总结给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据 SKILL.md，当前支持以下操作：\n\n## 1. 获取状态\n```bash\n$TOOL get_state\n```\n返回里程计、IMU、激光雷达、电池、运动模式等\n\n## 2. 控制运动\n```bash\n# 前进/后退\n$TOOL move --linear-x 0.5 --duration 2.0\n\n# 左转/右转\n$TOOL move --angular-z 1.0 --duration 1.0\n\n# 前进+转向（画弧）\n$TOOL move --linear-x 0.3 --angular-z -0.5 --duration 2.0\n\n# 横向平移（麦轮模式）\n$TOOL move --linear-y 0.3 --duration 1.0\n```\n\n## 3. 紧急停车\n```bash\n$TOOL stop\n```\n\n## 4. 导航\n```bash\n# 单点导航\n$TOOL navigate --x 1.0 --y 0.5 --yaw 1.57\n\n# 多点导航\n$TOOL navigate --waypoints \"1.0,0.0,0; 1.0,1.0,1.57; 0.0,0.0,3.14\"\n```\n\n## 5. 拍照\n```bash\n# 通过 WebSocket 获取摄像头图片\n$TOOL get_image\n\n# 通过 SSH 远程拍照\n$TOOL take_photo\n```\n\n---\n\n**注意**：阿克曼模式限制了原地转向能力。如果需要原地旋转，需要切换到**差速模式**或**麦轮模式**。\n\n需要我尝试其他操作吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1725,"output":431,"cacheRead":15488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774097243928}}
