{"type":"message","id":"cd80966b","parentId":"1675c240","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:50:30.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要让小车导航到前方放了黑色牌子的位置。这需要用到导航功能。\n\n但是首先我需要知道目标位置的坐标。用户说\"前方放了黑色牌子的位置\"，我没有这个位置的坐标信息。\n\n有几个选项：\n1. 先获取小车当前状态，看看激光雷达是否能检测到前方的物体\n2. 通过摄像头拍照看看前方的环境\n3. 询问用户目标位置的坐标\n\n我觉得应该先拍照看看环境，或者用激光雷达数据判断。让我先获取一下状态和拍照。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我需要先确认目标位置。让我拍照看看前方的环境："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_227258adaa6a49d791d93489","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"conda run -n mqtt-server python3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ROS-limo-car/scripts/limo_ws_client.py --host 172.31.94.183 get_image --output /tmp/limo_cam.jpg"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":12141,"output":281,"cacheRead":5504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17926,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774097420440}}
